{"tid":1509110,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有無人諗過，攬炒之後點？","createTime":"2019-08-26T17:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T04:39:00.000Z","uid":263448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"11a488d0ca73b392b999e88ff491f96569db4955","tid":1509110,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:24:55.000Z","msg":"我先假設，最後焦土派攬炒成功。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n習帝為咗威嚴、面子，決心同美國佬玩強。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共倒退，窮了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而係一直洗腦下，共民真係法西斯化、納稅化，未必會內亂架喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發窮惡既中共派兵攻打香港洩忿。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係無史架！<br />\n以前打完內戰，乜柒都無，唔怕死既人特別多！周圍打仗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察一定幫中共，但未必全身而退，因為平亂無功。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有理無理，先屠200萬人，沙田、黃大仙、深水埗、大埔，會有大災難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後係電腦秋後咩人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純討論"},{"pid":"1c362f3644b5e82084f2697135d8648c1fae3474","tid":1509110,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1ed732535fb60d671338f8fdf26f1698e380f228","tid":1509110,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":